products.title: Botanical Garden Rosella Multi Roman Blind
products.description: Lilies, bluebells, peonies, and all things flowery make up this botanical roman blind. With dragonflies, busy bees and delicate butterflies dotting this multicoloured roman blind, with splashes of warm yellows, purples and greens, this roman blind will look at home in your kitchen, office or bedroom. At swift direct blinds, quality is important to us, which is why your new roman blind comes with a fabulous five year guarantee, for extra peace of mind.
